DIGEST OF HB 1048 (Updated February 3, 2026 9:28 am - DI 140)
Citations Affected: IC 36-8.
Synopsis: VFD clothing and automobile allowances. Increases, from
$100 to $250, the clothing and automobile allowance for an active
member of a volunteer fire department.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
Novak, Pressel, Bartels, Moseley
(SENATE SPONSORS — CRIDER, POL JR., LEISING, BOHACEK,
NIEZGODSKI, FORD J.D.)
December 5, 2025, read first time and referred to Committee on Veterans Affairs and
Public Safety.
January 22, 2026, reported — Do Pass.
January 27, 2026, read second time, ordered engrossed.
January 28, 2026, engrossed. Read third time, passed. Yeas 89, nays 0.
SENATE ACTION
February 2, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Homeland Security and
Transportation.
February 3, 2026, reported favorably — Do Pass.
